This is how to generate_integers of a and b:
   Remember that lo is a
   Remember that hi is b
   When b is less than a, then:
      Remember that lo is b
      Remember that hi is a
   End when
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that x is lo
   Remember that limit is sum of hi and 1
   Do this limit times:
      When x is more than hi, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      When remainder of x and 2 is 0, then:
         Add result to x
      End when
      Increase x
   End do
   The answer is result
